title: Sidewall
description: Fruit, including grapes, peaches and cherries, sitting on napkin suspend from boss with anthemion and tassels. Acorn pendants hang from napkin corners. Small urn suspended from ribbons alternates with napkins. Printed in tan, black and white on pale green ground. Original document for "Offrande a Ceres."
